    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">Yes, all vehicles go through a basic inspection...</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">How does the auto bidding process work?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">Our system automatically places bids on your behalf up to your maximum bid amount. If you are the highest bidder when the auction ends, you win the item.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Can I cancel a bid after placing it?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">No, once a bid is placed, it cannot be canceled. Please review your bid carefully before confirming.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Do you offer financing for vehicles and engines?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">We do not provide direct financing, but you can use third-party financing options. Contact us for recommendations.</p>
  </div>
  <h1>Vehicle Sales</h1>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Are the vehicles inspected before being listed?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">Yes, all vehicles go through a basic inspection. However, we always recommend buyers inspect the vehicle themselves or hire a professional before bidding.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Do you provide vehicle history reports?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">Yes, we provide a history report for most vehicles. You can check the listing details or request one from our support team.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Are there any additional fees when purchasing a car?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">Yes, there may be auction fees, taxes, and title transfer fees. These are detailed at checkout.</p>
  </div>
  <h1>Engine Sales (Car, Truck & Boat)</h1>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Are the engines tested before sale?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">Most engines are tested and verified to be in working condition. The listing will specify if an engine has been tested.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Do you offer warranties on used engines?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">Some engines come with a limited warranty, but many are sold "as-is." Please check the listing details for warranty information.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Can I return an engine if it doesn’t fit my vehicle?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">Yes we accept returns for incorrect fitment. Please ensure compatibility before purchasing.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Do you ship engines, or is local pickup required?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">We offer both shipping and local pickup. Shipping costs vary based on location and engine size.</p>
  </div>
  <h1>Bidding & Payments</h1>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">How do I make a payment after winning a bid?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">You can pay via credit card, bank transfer, or PayPal. Full payment must be made within 48 hours of winning.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">What happens if I don’t pay after winning a bid?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">Failure to pay may result in account suspension and a penalty fee. Please bid responsibly.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Can I set an automatic bid limit?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">Yes, you can set a maximum bid, and our system will automatically bid for you until that amount is reached.</p>
  </div>
  <h1>Shipping & Pickup</h1>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Do you offer nationwide shipping for vehicles and engines?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden">Yes, we work with third-party shipping companies for nationwide delivery. Costs vary based on location and item size.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">Can I arrange my own shipping?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden"> Yes, you can arrange your own transportation if preferred.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">How long does it take to receive a shipped vehicle or engine?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden"> Delivery times depend on location and carrier availability. On average, shipping takes 7-14 days.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3 data-action="click->faq#toggle">What should I do if my shipment is delayed or lost?</h3>
    <p data-faq-target="answer" class="hidden"> Contact our support team, and we will assist in locating your shipment.</p>
  </div>
</div>
